com.businessglue.struts
Class TestAction

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.struts.action.Action
      com.businessglue.struts.TestAction
public class TestAction
extends org.apache.struts.action.Action

This class retieves a filename from the header, parses puts it in a FileBean and puts the bean in the session scope.

Workarounds include, path obtained by dubious methods (done in LoginAction), and file_name retrieved by parsing header, and not request.getHeader("filename")which returns null. The test_file_name used to be in the TestBean, but this cause null pointer exceptions for some reason, so all the variables needed are put in the session.
